STATE DETAILS
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

┌─ Idle
│  ├─ Description: Agent waiting or initialized state
│  ├─ Actions: None
│  ├─ Transitions:
│  │  └─ → Planning (when goal is set)
│  │  └─ → Executing (when plan already exists)
│  └─ Duration: Until goal provided

┌─ Planning
│  ├─ Description: Goal analysis & Task decomposition
│  ├─ Actions:
│  │  ├─ Analyze goal
│  │  ├─ Create task list
│  │  └─ Validate task feasibility
│  ├─ Transitions:
│  │  └─ → Executing (plan created)
│  │  └─ → Failed (impossible goal)
│  └─ Duration: Variable (logic dependent)

┌─ Executing
│  ├─ Description: Running current task
│  ├─ Actions:
│  │  ├─ Fetch current task
│  │  ├─ Call appropriate tool
│  │  └─ Update task status
│  ├─ Transitions:
│  │  └─ → Observing (task done)
│  │  └─ → Reflecting (task error)
│  └─ Duration: Task execution time

┌─ Observing
│  ├─ Description: Collecting and analyzing results
│  ├─ Actions:
│  │  ├─ Collect task output
│  │  ├─ Store to memory
│  │  └─ Validate result
│  ├─ Transitions:
│  │  └─ → Executing (more tasks)
│  │  └─ → Reflecting (unexpected result)
│  │  └─ → Completed (all done)
│  └─ Duration: Short (analysis time)

┌─ Reflecting
│  ├─ Description: Evaluating and adjusting strategy
│  ├─ Actions:
│  │  ├─ Analyze task result
│  │  ├─ Compare with expectations
│  │  └─ Decide next action
│  ├─ Transitions:
│  │  └─ → Planning (adjust strategy)
│  │  └─ → Executing (retry same task)
│  │  └─ → Completed (goal achieved)
│  │  └─ → Failed (give up)
│  └─ Duration: Evaluation time

┌─ Completed
│  ├─ Description: Goal successfully achieved
│  ├─ Actions: None
│  ├─ Transitions:
│  │  └─ → Idle (restart with new goal)
│  └─ Duration: Terminal state

┌─ Failed
│  ├─ Description: Goal cannot be achieved
│  ├─ Actions: None
│  ├─ Transitions:
│  │  └─ → Idle (restart with new goal)
│  └─ Duration: Terminal state


